<HEADLINE>
L.A. ECONOMY SIZZLES
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
BY GREGORY J. WILCOX 
c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES _ Los Angeles is moving into the millennium on a
roll.
</P>
<P>
   Despite impending job cutbacks in the aerospace sector, Southern
