<DOCNO> NYT19990729.0041 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-29 02:29 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8182 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BBA-REDSOX-GORDON-BOS     07-29 1630
