<P>
   MOVIES-BESTSOFAR _ End-of-the-decade years have often been huge
at the movies: ``Gone with the Wind'' and ``Stagecoach'' in 1939,
``Ben-Hur'' and ``The Diary of Anne Frank'' in 1959, ``Apocolypse
Now'' and ``Alien'' in 1979. We present a signature column on best
movies so far for 1999, likely to include ``October Sky,''
``Election,'' ``The Matrix,'' ``Blair Witch Project'' and others
and assessing what kind of year this is. (StMurray, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   EDs: EMBARGOED UNTIL SUNDAY, AUG. 1
