   HANDYMAN-HOTTON (Undated) _ Don't replace those three-year-old
shingles. The streaks on them may be removable. By Petere Hotton.
</P>
<P>
   WHITE-COLUMN (Undated) _ ``Antiques Roadshow'' is trash without
guilt. It's the ``Masterpiece Theater'' version of ``Let's Make a
Deal.'' I'm addicted. By Diane White.
</P>
