or coming that not only make your work life go more smoothly, but
are fun to use. By David Armstrong. 1330 words.
</P>
<P>
   TECHNO-PHONES (Undated) _ Phone makers are churning out a lot of
high-powered hardware that could give your briefcase a higher IQ
than your brain. By Hiawatha Bray. 1030 words.
</P>
