<P>
   Here are the stories New York Times editors are planning for
Page 1, Friday, July 30. The N.Y. Times News Service Night
Supervisor is Pat Ryan; phone: (888) 346-9867; e-mail:
patryan(at)nytimes.com.
</P>
<P>
   TOP
</P>
<P>
   Lead story:
</P>
<P>
   GA-SHOOT (Atlanta) _ Ledeall: A man identified as a day trader
went on a rampage at a brokerage office, killing at least nine
people. Police said the gunman, who remains at large, also shot
three relatives at a house in a suburb south of Atlanta.
Developing. By Kevin Sack. (We plan to move the story by 9 p.m. ET
in ``a'' news file.) 1,400 words.
</P>
