</P>
<P>
   SEATTLE-SIDRAN (Seattle) _ It's a struggle for nothing less than
the hearts, minds and good manners of Seattle, and Mark Sidran is
more than willing to wage war. Sidran, the three-term Seattle city
attorney, has been on the forefront of efforts to enforce a civil
atmosphere in the city, from lying on downtown sidewalks to noisy
nightclubs that keep neighbors up to panhandlers that frighten and
intimidate people on the street.
