Fahrenheit. Przybocki said that people were bringing her bottled
water and was grateful for their help. Chicago opened over 100
cooling centers to help allieviete the heat for locals without air
conditioning. (Todd Buchanan Jul 29, 1999. (Todd Buchanan/New York
Times Photo)
